================================================================================
Third-party content fetched at runtime
================================================================================

This package fetches the OAK (OnChain Attack Knowledge) framework
content snapshot — Tactics, Techniques, Mitigations, Software, worked
examples, and the relationships between them — at runtime from
https://onchainattack.org/tools/embedded.json and caches it locally
on disk under the platform cache directory.

The OAK framework and its associated documentation are produced by the
OAK project at https://onchainattack.org and the upstream repository
https://github.com/onchainattack/oak, and are licensed under the
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License
(CC-BY-SA 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

